&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;Levanta is the leading affiliate marketing platform for marketplace sellers, helping Amazon, Shopify and Walmart brands unlock a scalable, cost-effective marketing channel through direct affiliate partnerships. With access to over 70,000 vetted publishers, influencers, affiliates, and media buyers in Levanta’s Creator Marketplace, sellers can drive high-quality external traffic to their stores, control commissions, improve organic search rankings, and benefit from referral kickbacks on sales generated by their affiliates.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;We are seeking a Customer Success Manager based in Asia to join our team and support our growing presence in the region. In this role, fluency in Mandarin (spoken and written) is essential for serving our Chinese-speaking sellers and agency partners. You will be the main point of contact for these clients, helping drive satisfaction, retention, and growth through a deep understanding of their goals and how Levanta’s platform can help them succeed.&lt;/p&gt;
