&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;Levanta is the leading affiliate marketing platform for marketplace sellers, helping Amazon, Shopify and Walmart brands unlock a scalable, cost-effective marketing channel through direct affiliate partnerships. With access to over 70,000 vetted publishers, influencers, affiliates, and media buyers in Levanta’s Creator Marketplace, sellers can drive high-quality external traffic to their stores, control commissions, improve organic search rankings, and benefit from referral kickbacks on sales generated by their affiliates.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;Levanta is hiring its first Head of Legal to lead legal across the business. This person will be a strategic partner to the CEO, executive team, and board, while also being highly hands-on in the day-to-day legal needs of a fast-moving startup.&lt;/p&gt;
