&lt;li&gt;Identify potential clients and key decision-makers through research, networking, and cold outreach.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Utilize various tools and strategies to generate and qualify new leads.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Outbound and Inbound Sales Activities:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Conduct high-volume outbound prospecting (email, phone, and LinkedIn) to engage potential customers.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Respond to and qualify inbound leads generated by marketing campaigns.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Pipeline Management:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage and maintain a pipeline of interested prospects and engage them effectively to convert into sales opportunities.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Use CRM software to track and manage leads, ensuring accurate and up-to-date information.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Collaborate with Sales Team:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work closely with Account Executives to set up meetings and follow up on leads.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide detailed notes and insights to support the sales process.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Continuous Improvement:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
